WEBVTT

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:04.136
In a few hours, I saw 
that the children were surfing the net.

00:02:04.160 --> 00:02:07.456
People said, "They don’t know English,
so how are they surfing?"

00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:10.836
I said, "I do not have any idea."

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:16.190
After two days, they had downloaded
and installed a game and were playing!

00:02:16.190 --> 00:02:18.080
(Laughter)

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:20.649
Everyone was like,
“Where did they learn that?”

00:02:20.681 --> 00:02:22.176
I said, “I have no clue.”

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:23.776
About three months later,

00:02:23.801 --> 00:02:26.936
the school teacher asked me,

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:28.910
“What have you done to these children?”

00:02:28.910 --> 00:02:30.296
I asked “Why, what happened?”